output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF presence: Yes, CMF 11240014 is present, indicating this is electoral content.
2. Candidate reference: - Mentions "George Simion" in the title - George Simion is a presidential candidate (Position 2) - Also mentions Ovidiu Cupșa, an AUR Senate candidate
3. Wide population targeting: - This is a paid advertisement on Facebook and Instagram - Has reached between 25,000-29,999 impressions - Targets a potential audience of over 1 million people
4. Electoral objective: - The title "Susține George Simion Județul Constanta" is a clear call for support - Links to political content "POLITICA ÎN AFACERI" - Features a Senate candidate from the same party
5. Journalism check: - This appears to be campaign content rather than journalistic material - The presence of CMF and party attribution confirms this is campaign material
6. Personal opinion: - This is not a personal opinion but an official party communication

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It explicitly promotes George Simion, a presidential candidate - Contains official campaign elements (CMF number) - Is a paid advertisement reaching a wide audience - Has clear electoral objectives - Is commissioned by AUR ("Comandat de Alianta Pentru Unirea Romanilor")
conclusion.message-for-police: Alianta pentru Unirea Romanilor (AUR), pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui material de propaganda electorala pentru candidatul prezidential George Nicolae Simion dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie electorala. Materialul, cu ID-ul facebook 562641266468758, postat dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, constituie propaganda electorala prin faptul ca promoveaza explicit candidatul ("Susține George Simion Județul Constanta"), contine numar CMF (11240014), este platit pentru a ajunge la un public larg (25,000-29,999 impresii), si are obiectiv electoral explicit de sustinere a candidatului la presedintie. Materialul este comandat oficial de catre partid, conform mentiunii "Comandat de Alianta Pentru Unirea Romanilor".
